snippet.title: BLINDFIRE - PlayStation Release Trailer
snippet.description:
🎮 Get it on PlayStation now: https://gsght.com/c/gac7o5 
PlayStation Plus 10% off Nov 21st - Dec 9th
⏱︎  Early Access Game. Get instant access and start playing; get involved with this game as it develops.

🌃 Blindfire delivers unique FPS action in pitch-black arenas. Rely on sound and high-tech gadgets to develop your skills in new ways. Ideal for quick, high-tension matches with friends.
